flowchart TB
    N1["1. neo-bridge-watcher-eth: Proof/evidence flow shows how a claim becomes checkable."]
    N2["2. Claim: This unit performed: Filter bridge events | Normalize payloads | Protect replay/cursor state."]
    N3["3. Witness or input: ETH RPC/log stream | bridge contract events | checkpoint cursor"]
    N4["4. Execution or check: verify source event, confirmations, nonce, asset action, and target message"]
    N5["5. Public commitment: message hash, nonce, source height, and asset action"]
    N6["6. Verifier: gateway | shared bridge | operator dashboard"]
    N7["7. Accepted result: relay job | audit log | health metric"]
    N8["8. Rejected result: drop or quarantine message; nonce and asset state do not advance"]
    N1 --> N2
    N2 --> N3
    N3 --> N4
    N4 --> N5
    N5 --> N6
    N6 --> N7
    N7 --> N8
